<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #374151; color: white; padding: 25px; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; text-align: center; }
    .content { background: #f9fafb; padding: 25px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-top: none; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
    .info-box { background: #f0f9ff; border: 1px solid #bae6fd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .access-info { background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .cta-button { display: inline-block; padding: 14px 28px; background: #1e40af; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #9ca3af; font-size: 12px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1 style="margin: 0;">Subscription Cancelled</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>Hi <%= @tenant.company_name %>,</p>

    <p>We're sorry to see you go. Your Pharma Transport subscription has been cancelled as requested.</p>

    <div class="access-info">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">What happens next?</h3>

      <p><strong>Access until:</strong> <%= @access_until&.strftime("%B %d, %Y") || "End of billing period" %></p>

      <p>You'll continue to have full access to your account until this date. After that:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Real-time monitoring will be disabled</li>
        <li>API access will be revoked</li>
        <li>Your audit trail data will be retained for compliance (7 years)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="info-box">
      <strong>ðŸ“‹ Export Your Data</strong><br>
      Before your access ends, you may want to export your compliance reports and audit logs. Visit your dashboard to download your data.
    </div>

    <p>Changed your mind? You can resubscribe at any time to restore full access.</p>

    <p style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="<%= @resubscribe_url %>" class="cta-button">Resubscribe Now</a>
    </p>

    <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">
      We'd love to hear your feedback. If there's anything we could have done better, please reply to this email and let us know.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>Pharma Transport - FDA 21 CFR Part 11 Compliant</p>
    <p>Your audit data is retained for regulatory compliance.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
